In the distance Prebon watched the scanners, he carefully monitored the
battle between the Alliance and the Maximals." Trainers, report to my office
for orders." he decided to let the Alliance take care of the Maximals then
go after whoevers left.

Bullet was the first to reply, "On my way lord Prebon."

Ignatius was refueling at the time so he couldn't go right away. "I'll be up
soon as possible."

Blaze was monitoring communications so she was already outside his office.

Hammer was outside playing in the sand in Grizzly bear mode. "Yes Sir.:"

(This means Slayer too.)
